\newlabel{fig:recursive_vs_true}{{8}{25}{Recursive (CG-internal) versus true residual $\|b-Ax\|$ on the real $16^4$ configuration. The recursive curves of all precisions overlap; only the true-residual floor separates by $\uu $, directly exhibiting the reach-versus-rate distinction}{figure.8}{}}
